strings: <voice_0x0100174D><se_low>King Trode: It's been a long journey.

<voice_0x0100174E><se_low>King Trode: A lot has happened along the way,
but it's all worked out well in the end.
<voice_0x0100174F><se_low>King Trode: Old obligations matter not one jot. What matters is being able to live a full and happy life.

<voice_0x01001750><se_low>King Trode: You should decide for yourself who
you wish to marry. I won't rush you.
Take as long as you need.
<voice_0x01001751><se_low>King Trode: Although, I don't know how easy it will be to find someone now that you've jilted a prince...

<voice_0x01001752><se_high>Princess Medea: Never mind that now, Father. Look! We're home!
Home for good!
